      <p>Standard parameter uses the Standard algorithm to normalize this dimension for rows or columns, i.e., each row or column is subtracted from the data minimum and divided by the data maximum. The formula is:<disp-formula id="deqn02"><tex-math notation="LaTeX" id="DmEquation2">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
